{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"449d0144-69d5-4bc2-a7bf-9442a94729b9","content":"No files found in the working directory. I'll provide you with the pattern for converting your page to compiled bindings.\n\n## Converting to Compiled Bindings\n\nAdd `x:DataType` to your `ContentPage` root element pointing to your ViewModel:\n\n```xml\n<ContentPage xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n             xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n             xmlns:vm=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.ViewModels\"\n             x:Class=\"YourApp.Views.SettingsPage\"\n             x:DataType=\"vm:SettingsViewModel\">\n\n    <VerticalStackLayout>\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding Theme}\" />\n        <Switch IsToggled=\"{Binding NotificationsEnabled}\" />\n        <Label Text=\"{Binding FontSize}\" />\n    </VerticalStackLayout>\n</ContentPage>\n```\n\n## Catching Binding Errors at Build Time\n\nOnce `x:DataType` is declared, the XAML compiler validates all `{Binding}` paths against the specified type. To ensure errors surface at build:\n\n1. **Enable XamlC** (on by default in .NET MAUI, but you can be explicit):\n   ```csharp\n   [assembly: XamlCompilation(XamlCompilationOptions.Compile)]\n   ```\n\n2. **Set `WarningsAsErrors`** in your `.csproj` for binding-related warnings:\n   ```xml\n   <PropertyGroup>\n     <WarningsAsErrors>$(WarningsAsErrors);XC0045</WarningsAsErrors>\n   </PropertyGroup>\n   ```\n   `XC0045` is emitted when a binding path doesn't resolve against the `x:DataType`.\n\n3. **Avoid `x:DataType=\"\"` overrides** — setting it to an empty string disables compiled bindings for that scope (useful only for dynamic scenarios like `DataTemplateSelector`).\n\nWith `x:DataType` in place, a typo like `{Binding Themee}` will now produce a **build error** instead of silently failing at runtime.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"278b80ca-cec7-4dc6-ad0c-4761d97fd0dc","outputTokens":511,"requestId":"081B:37A92F:A12665:BA9BEF:69F2A7B0"},"id":"a8a24f65-8ebe-450e-b5d4-45292f491209","timestamp":"2026-04-30T00:52:10.893Z","parentId":"49dbb16c-de12-4239-85b3-ec6b9402fede"}
